analysis.heading: Attached garages/carports site planning
analysis.content: Attached garages must comply with same setbacks as main dwelling. Note: Uncovered spaces must be located beyond the required frontyard and beyond the first 10' of the street-side yard.
figures: Fig 33. Examples of site planning solutions for attached garages/carports showing interior lot examples and corner lot example with diagrams for: A) 1-car garage with 2nd space (uncovered) located in the sideyard, B) 1-car garage with 2nd space (uncovered) located in the driveway, C) 2-car garage with no uncovered spaces
